		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-start-api-v1",
		"name": "Start API (AgroBozor)",
		"description": "## Postman da testlash\n\n### 1. O'zgaruvchilar (Variables)\nCollection ustiga o'ng tugma → **Edit** → **Variables** yoki asosiy sahifada **Variables**.\n- **baseUrl**: API manzili, oxirida `/api/v1` bo'lsin.\n  - OSPanel/virtual host: `http://SIZNING-DOMEN/api/v1`\n  - `php artisan serve`: `http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1`\n- **token**: boshida bo'sh. Login dan keyin to'ldirasiz.\n\n### 2. Token olish tartibi\n1. **Auth → Login** so'rovini yuboring (telefon va parol to'g'ri bo'lsin).\n2. Javob JSON ichidan `access_token` (yoki loyihadagi token maydoni nomi) ni ko'ring.\n3. **token** o'zgaruvchiga nusxa qiling (Collection yoki Environment).\n4. JWT talab qilinadigan so'rovlar (Ads papkasi) endi ishlaydi.\n\n### 3. Tokensiz endpointlar\n**Public** va **Resources** papkalarida **Authorization: No Auth** — alohida token shart emas.\n- Public: barcha faol e'lonlar, bitta e'lon.\n- Resources: viloyat, tuman, kategoriya, subkategoriya.\n\n### 4. O'z rekalalari CRUD (JWT)\nBarcha amallar **`/profile/ads`** ostida (`apiResource`), alohida `/ads` yo'q.\n- **GET** `/profile/ads` — ro'yxat\n- **POST** `/profile/ads` — yaratish (form-data tavsiya)\n- **GET** `/profile/ads/1` — bitta (URLda `1` = e'lon ID; Laravel yo'l nomi `ad`)\n- **PUT** yoki **PATCH** `/profile/ads/1` — yangilash\n- **DELETE** `/profile/ads/1` — o'chirish\nProfilda **region_id** va **city_id** bo'lmasa POST 422 beradi.\n\n### 5. Kutiladigan kodlar\n- **200** — muvaffaqiyatli GET.\n- **201** — yaratildi (POST profile/ads).\n- **401** — token yo'q/noto'g'ri.\n- **404** — resurs topilmadi.\n- **422** — validatsiya yoki profil manzili to'liq emas.\n\n### 6. Sarlavhalar\nHar so'rovda: **Accept: application/json** (kolleksiyada qo'yilgan).\nJSON yuborishda: **Content-Type: application/json**.\n\n### Swagger\nBrauzer: `{sayt}/api/documentation`. Yangilash: `composer run swagger` yoki `php artisan l5-swagger:generate`.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"variable": [
